name: The rolling stones
description: It was Hediye's lighter. Hediye means gift in farsi. she was a very young waitress in the cafe I used to work in, and she had a great passion for music. Hediye still keeps this lighter because it reminds her of her first boyfriend. i was cafe's dishwasher and I drew this in my break time on my sony Xperia LT26i scrached screen using andriod paintfree app. no layers, no photo transforms.because the app has a limited size i just took screenshot of my work.
